  <entry>
    <title>Hexo 發布到 Github 小筆記</title>
    <link href="http://antfire70007.github.io/2019/02/03/hexo-plus-github/"/>
    <id>http://antfire70007.github.io/2019/02/03/hexo-plus-github/</id>
    <published>2019-02-03T03:17:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-02-03T04:23:05.184Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="建立-Github-Repository"><a href="#建立-Github-Repository" class="headerlink" title="建立 Github Repository"></a>建立 Github Repository</h1><p>先登入<a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Github</a><br>接著<a href="https://github.com/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">建立Repository傳送門</a><br>需注意的是 Repository名稱必須是&lt;帳號名稱&gt;.github.io，<br>例如您的帳號是 “HandsomeMan” 那麼您的Repository名稱就必須設定為 “HandsomeMan.github.io”</p><h1 id="Clone-Repository"><a href="#Clone-Repository" class="headerlink" title="Clone Repository"></a>Clone Repository</h1><p>使用Git指令將剛才的Repository 複製回來</p><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/YOUR-REPOSITORY</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以步驟1的例子為例:</p><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/HandsomeMan/HandsomeMan.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="設定Github-SSH-Key"><a href="#設定Github-SSH-Key" class="headerlink" title="設定Github SSH Key"></a>設定Github SSH Key</h1><ol><li>複製回來後，<code>cd</code>指令切換目錄到剛剛複製下來的專案資料夾底下</li></ol><ol><li><p>使用 <code>ssh-keygen</code> 產生 RSA Key</p><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C handsome@yourgithubaccount.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>將<code>C:\Users\&lt;YourAccount&gt;\.ssh\id_rsa.pub</code>的內容複製到github設定底下</p></li><li><p>點擊 Add Key</p></li><li><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.email &lt;yourgithubemail&gt; </span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name &lt;yourgithubname&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接著會有提示輸入，要記得輸入 <code>yes</code></p><h1 id="安裝-Hexo"><a href="#安裝-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安裝 Hexo"></a>安裝 Hexo</h1><ol><li><code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code></li></ol></li></ol><ol><li>切換目錄至專案目錄底下 <figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="調整Hexo設定"><a href="#調整Hexo設定" class="headerlink" title="調整Hexo設定"></a>調整Hexo設定</h1><ol><li><p>修改<code>_config.yml</code></p></li><li><p>設定deploy參數<br>找到deploy區塊<br>將type的值改為<code>git</code><br>並且將repo改為Github Repository位址<br><code>repo:https://github.com/HandsomeMan/HandsomeMan.github.io</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">  deploy:</span><br><span class="line">type: git</span><br><span class="line">repo: https://github.com/HandsomeMan/HandsomeMan.github.io</span><br><span class="line">branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="新增文章"><a href="#新增文章" class="headerlink" title="新增文章"></a>新增文章</h1><ol><li>輸入 <code>hexo new post &lt;title&gt;</code></li></ol><h1 id="預覽結果"><a href="#預覽結果" class="headerlink" title="預覽結果"></a>預覽結果</h1><pre><code><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate # or hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo server  # or hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><h1 id="將Hexo發佈到Github"><a href="#將Hexo發佈到Github" class="headerlink" title="將Hexo發佈到Github"></a>將Hexo發佈到Github</h1><ol><li>安裝 <code>Hexo Deployer Git</code><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><ol><li>執行<code>hexo deploy</code><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy # or hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h1><p><a href="https://my.oschina.net/yizongjishi/blog/1862148" target="_blank" rel="noopener">oschina</a><br><a href="https://alumincan.github.io/2017/03/28/setup-blog-on-github/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">alumincan</a>    </p>]]></content>
    
